Platform Notes
--------------

  Linux 64-bit
  * mongo (the shell) is a 32-bit binary even on 64-bit linux.  This is because of of v8 - which only works 32bit
    to run you'll need to make sure you have 32 bits stdc++  some common names: lib32stdc++6, libstdc++.i386
